{"tid":901091,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"家用NAS有咩用途?","createTime":"2018-11-13T17:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T06:29:30.000Z","uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b41c62afde45360075ab5b58e42353f24be54c","tid":901091,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"非挑戰<br />\n因為屋企有部ds412+<br />\n但平時拎來又冇用<br />\n見到格離post有人問自己砌nas<br />\n想問下各位巴打屋企部nas拎來做咩?<br />\n<br />\n暫時有用來bt, 但唔知邊度搵種好<br />\n想睇中台美劇+電影"},{"pid":"4cadfdd9a66fecbf4347044044ebdf14d4aa6dea","tid":901091,"uid":47480,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:31:40.000Z","msg":"擺av"},{"pid":"f0b5a42426dac46295a23e04168f6d4fcffbe3f7","tid":901091,"uid":6513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"放相 Backup File(Local / Cloud)<br />\nDown野 做media server"},{"pid":"b54b5fb7f54fd6179a2829aa0d55d667062a3981","tid":901091,"uid":23094,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"擺歌 擺戲<br />\nWeb server<br />\nMedia server<br />\n私家Cloud<br />\nBackup<br />\n玩VM<br />\n最緊要係有Parity disk預防死HDD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e010b0e270b553bef486d6467f578b5c12cdea","tid":901091,"uid":1402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你諗到既都做得 應該係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c2d9b77b47fff809d739fef751e0527032ce9c","tid":901091,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T18:18:12.000Z","msg":"無用，$10 收你"},{"pid":"583359453286dc3a328f5123402eb03bf34ad719","tid":901091,"uid":1085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T18:35:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5ebf5404540f66ef32c6e54143d2d14f988ff09","tid":901091,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T18:39:51.000Z","msg":"如果做backup既<br />\n<br />\n平時用harddisk一定要帶住舊野黎back<br />\n<br />\n如果用nas就唔洗<br />\n<br />\n比如你電腦係A地點 NAS係B地點<br />\n<br />\n你可以用vpn連去B地點再連去NAS做backup<br />\n<br />\n相對地比起你用harddisk係A地點backup安全得多同埋方便<br />\n<br />\n因為如果你屋企火燭 咁你個harddisk都無用<br />\n<br />\n除非你每次backup完就將個harddisk拎去B地點<br />\n<br />\n但咁就勁麻煩<br />\n<br />\n不過其實依家asus有d router都可以插harddisk做雲端<br />\n<br />\n所以如果純粹用黎做backup其實真係無咩必要"},{"pid":"14f9a6cbb56b7481f775fe8e38df3aef1101150c","tid":901091,"uid":79481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b54b5fb7f54fd6179a2829aa0d55d667062a3981","tid":901091,"uid":23094,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"擺歌 擺戲<br />\nWeb server<br />\nMedia server<br />\n私家Cloud<br />\nBackup<br />\n玩VM<br />\n最緊要係有Parity disk預防死HDD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T18:43:30.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n<br />\n你電腦有一份 nas有一份<br />\n<br />\n如果兩份都咁黑仔一齊死<br />\n<br />\n你行raid 1都一樣死喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda4b27c9f78bd802ad252ce96cedcad1d57e88c","tid":901091,"uid":169435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T18:56:34.000Z","msg":"用windows pc直接放file係冇問題<br />\n不過用nas,中毒機會少D<br />\n你用手機/ipad睇片方便D<br />\n<br />\n佔位細個 destop<br />\n你用nas，可玩notebook+nas  vs destop大大件<br />\n<br />\n管理hdd方便D<br />\netc你要行hdtune/smart   pc可能2xhr不能reboot<br />\nnas就由佢run<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nnas唔係必需，不過$2000-3000上下，有需要ipad睇片，就好值得買"},{"pid":"9e506e121bf73d198a1cf963b5358063ad93bc74","tid":901091,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dda4b27c9f78bd802ad252ce96cedcad1d57e88c","tid":901091,"uid":169435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T18:56:34.000Z","msg":"用windows pc直接放file係冇問題<br />\n不過用nas,中毒機會少D<br />\n你用手機/ipad睇片方便D<br />\n<br />\n佔位細個 destop<br />\n你用nas，可玩notebook+nas  vs destop大大件<br />\n<br />\n管理hdd方便D<br />